<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:47:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国贸易办公室和乔·拜登在最新的贸易战中瞄准了中国的钢铁、海运和物流行业</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259375/us-trade-office-and-joe-biden-target-chinas-steel-maritime-and-logistics-sectors-latest-trade-war?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>美国总统乔·拜登呼吁对中国钢铁和铝征收三倍关税，而美国贸易代表办公室对北京在物流和造船业的做法展开调查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 13:57:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259375/us-trade-office-and-joe-biden-target-chinas-steel-maritime-and-logistics-sectors-latest-trade-war?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>高级经济学家表示，中国经济出现“巨变”和失衡，出乎北京方面的预料</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3259351/chinas-economy-seeing-seismic-shifts-and-imbalances-nothing-beijing-predicted-senior-economist-says?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>著名政府顾问刘元春表示，在第一季度GDP增长令人印象深刻之后，不久的将来将出现失衡，非经济风险将多于经济风险。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 13:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3259351/chinas-economy-seeing-seismic-shifts-and-imbalances-nothing-beijing-predicted-senior-economist-says?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着国内竞争加剧，中国电动汽车制造商东风汽车和奇瑞汽车将目光投向欧洲工厂</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3259355/chinese-ev-makers-dongfeng-motor-and-chery-automobile-eye-factories-europe-competition-escalates?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>东风、奇瑞和比亚迪等汽车制造商正着眼于欧洲的生产基地来组装下一代电动汽车，以对抗欧盟的保护主义关税，因为国内残酷的价格战迫使更多生产商到海外寻找新市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:32:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/china-business/article/3259355/chinese-ev-makers-dongfeng-motor-and-chery-automobile-eye-factories-europe-competition-escalates?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>国防部长通话后，中美两国是否会改变在南海的方针？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3259363/will-us-and-china-change-course-south-china-sea-after-defence-ministers-call?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>董军和劳埃德·奥斯汀之间的通话是在中国海警与美国盟友菲律宾发生一系列冲突之后发出的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:20:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3259363/will-us-and-china-change-course-south-china-sea-after-defence-ministers-call?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国集结航空人才让宽体C929起飞，增强空客和波音的竞争</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259340/china-rallies-aviation-brainpower-get-widebody-c929-ground-amp-airbus-and-boeing-competition?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国国有飞机制造商在为期一周的研讨会之前召开了一次会议，寻求其 C929 客机的进展，该客机将在长途航线上与空客 A350 和波音 787 机型竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 10:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259340/china-rallies-aviation-brainpower-get-widebody-c929-ground-amp-airbus-and-boeing-competition?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国国有企业同意向尼日尔军政府提供4亿美元贷款以换取石油</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259074/chinese-state-firm-agrees-us400m-loan-niger-junta-return-oil?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>利用资源偿还贷款是中国流行的模式，但批评者警告说，这些交易不公平，并且“抵押了国家的未来”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 10:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259074/chinese-state-firm-agrees-us400m-loan-niger-junta-return-oil?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国制定三年计划，建设数字劳动力并克服赢得科技竞赛所需的劳动力短缺</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3259326/china-lays-out-3-year-plan-build-digital-workforce-and-overcome-shortfall-workers-needed-win-tech?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>除了工业和教育项目外，还鼓励地方政府提供福利，包括住房激励、创业投资以及数字工作者家庭的教育和就业机会。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:07:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3259326/china-lays-out-3-year-plan-build-digital-workforce-and-overcome-shortfall-workers-needed-win-tech?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着对叛乱的担忧加剧，中国在缅甸边境再次举行实弹演习</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3259318/china-conducts-second-live-fire-drill-along-myanmar-border-month-concerns-over-rebel-uprisings-grow?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>人民解放军在三兄弟联盟与缅甸军政府的战斗中举行防空演习。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 08:31:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/military/article/3259318/china-conducts-second-live-fire-drill-along-myanmar-border-month-concerns-over-rebel-uprisings-grow?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>两名中国顶尖学者因“打招呼”被反腐人士点名羞辱</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3259291/2-top-chinese-academics-named-and-shamed-graft-busters-saying-hello?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>获奖科学家季洁、杨丽君试图利用个人关系获取政府研究经费而被捕。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 07:44:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3259291/2-top-chinese-academics-named-and-shamed-graft-busters-saying-hello?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>德国总理肖尔茨访华显示欧盟在如何与北京就贸易和俄罗斯问题进行接触方面存在分歧</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259275/visit-china-german-chancellor-scholz-shows-divisions-eu-over-how-engage-beijing-trade-and-russia?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在中国的公开讲话中，德国总理并未支持布鲁塞尔的去风险议程，而是主要关注德国的商业利益。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 04:42:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3259275/visit-china-german-chancellor-scholz-shows-divisions-eu-over-how-engage-beijing-trade-and-russia?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着中国研究的撤退让银行和经纪商感到寒意，价值数百万美元的工作、旅行福利和热闹的派对都消失了</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3259271/million-dollar-jobs-travel-perks-and-racy-parties-vanish-chinas-research-pullback-sends-chills?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>知情人士称，此次削减是由于市场长期低迷导致交易佣金减少，而且当局收紧了对分析师可以发表的研究的限制。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 04:30:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3259271/million-dollar-jobs-travel-perks-and-racy-parties-vanish-chinas-research-pullback-sends-chills?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>报告警告称，到2030年，中国数据中心和人工智能行业的用水量可能会超过韩国人口规模</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3259230/chinas-growing-data-centres-and-ai-industry-could-strain-scarce-water-resources-according-new-report?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>香港智库表示，到 2030 年，中国数据设施的年用水量（其中近一半位于干旱地区）可能会增加一倍以上，而人工智能聊天机器人则“饮用大量的水”来冷却自己。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 02:00:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/science/article/3259230/chinas-growing-data-centres-and-ai-industry-could-strain-scarce-water-resources-according-new-report?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着出口增长，中国在“数字丝绸之路”论坛上强调阿里巴巴和Shein在促进跨境电子商务方面的作用</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3259236/china-plays-alibaba-sheins-role-promoting-cross-border-e-commerce-digital-silk-road-forum-exports?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在西安举行的数字丝绸之路发展论坛上，阿里巴巴和Shein因帮助推动中国蓬勃发展的跨境电子商务行业而受到赞扬。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 01:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3259236/china-plays-alibaba-sheins-role-promoting-cross-border-e-commerce-digital-silk-road-forum-exports?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国GDP：第一季度增长“粉碎”预期，但北京是否在篮子里放了太多鸡蛋？</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3259182/china-gdp-first-quarter-growth-smashes-expectations-has-beijing-put-too-many-eggs-its-basket?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>中国今年前三个月备受关注的国内生产总值(GDP)数据超出预期，但3月份零售销售增速下降，第一季度房地产投资下降9.5%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 23:00:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/economic-indicators/article/3259182/china-gdp-first-quarter-growth-smashes-expectations-has-beijing-put-too-many-eggs-its-basket?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>广交会：订单激增，中国新能源出口企业热闹非凡，贸易限制威胁隐现</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259206/canton-fair-chinas-new-energy-exporters-abuzz-orders-swell-threat-trade-curbs-looms?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着订单的增加，广交会上新能源设备的买家和参展商表现出无限的乐观情绪，但美国和欧盟可能采取的针对该行业的措施可能会破坏这一乐趣。</description><pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 22:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3259206/canton-fair-chinas-new-energy-exporters-abuzz-orders-swell-threat-trade-curbs-looms?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item></channel></rss>